#### Feature Description

Option to set the player parameters that need to be used. See documentation (https://developers.google.com/youtube/player_parameters.html?playerVersion=HTML5#Parameters)

```
new YT.Player(this.playerId, {
            playerVars: { <--- this is missing -->
                playsinline: 1
            },
            videoId: this.id,
            height: '1920px',
            width: '1080px',
            events: {
                'onReady': () => {
                },                
               'onStateChange': (event) => {
                }
            }
        })
```
